<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
  <%- include('partials/template/head.ejs')  %>
</head>

<body>
  <div class="flex justify-center h-60 overflow-hidden bg-gray-900">
    <img class="h-72 -mt-4" src="/images/tompetty-heartbreakers-logo.png" alt="">
  </div>
  <nav class="bg-gray-800 text-white">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-2 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="flex items-center justify-between h-16">
        <div id="logo" class="font-logo text-sm sm:text-2xl ml-2">
          Tom Petty
        </div>
        <ul class="flex flex-row space-x-1 sm:space-x-2 items-center text-lg">
          <li class="flex items-center h-10 px-2 sm:px-5 rounded-md hover:bg-gray-700"><a href="/">Home</a></li>
          <li class="flex items-center h-10 px-2 sm:px-5 rounded hover:bg-gray-700"><a href="/albums">Albums</a></li>
          <li class="active-page flex items-center h-10 px-2 sm:px-5 rounded hover:bg-gray-700"><a href="/forum">Forum</a></li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </nav>
  <div class="min-h-screen bg-gray-400">
    <div id="inner-container" class="flex mx-auto flex-col items-center bg-gray-200 max-w-7xl min-h-screen">
      <h1 class="text-6xl font-serif mt-6">Forum</h1>
      <div id="input-comment-and-show-comments" class="flex flex-row justify-between p-6 space-x-2 w-full">
        <form id="forum-form" action="" class="w-1/3 p-1">
          <div>Name</div>
          <input type="text" name="name" id="name" placeholder="Your Name" class="p-1 mt-1 w-full"><br>
          <div class="mt-2">Comment</div>
          <textarea name="comment" id="comment" placeholder="Your comment" cols="30" rows="5" class="p-1 mt-1 w-full"></textarea>
          <div class="w-full flex justify-end">
            <input type="submit" class="py-2 px-5 rounded shadow">
          </div>
        </form>
        <div id="comments" class="w-2/3 px-4 py-2 space-y-3">
          <div class="commentGroup">
            <div class="name-and-time flex justify-between">
              <div class="name font-bold">tompettyfan123</div>
              <div class="time">7:05p</div>
            </div>
            <div class="comment">Lorem ipsum dolor, sit amet consectetur adipisicing elit. Culpa sunt illum doloribus iste et libero suscipit aliquid est distinctio cupiditate nam eveniet hic totam necessitatibus sapiente, ducimus eum rem inventore nostrum cum, officia atque consectetur, amet eligendi. Porro, commodi fuga!</div>
          </div>
          <div class="comment"></div>
          <div class="comment"></div>
          <div class="comment"></div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <%- include('partials/template/jsdefault.ejs') %> 

<script src="js/forum.js"></script>
</body>

</html>